org.sakaiproject.entitybroker.collector

Interface AutoRegister

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AutoRegisterEntityProvider, OrderedBean
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnnouncementEntityProviderImpl, AssignmentEntityProviderImpl, BLTIEventsEntityProvider, ChatChannelEntityProvider, ChatMessageEntityProvider, ForumEntityProviderImpl, ForumMessageEntityProviderImpl, ForumTopicEntityProviderImpl, LessonBuilderEntityProducer, MatrixCellEntityProviderImpl, PCServiceEntityProvider, ProfileEntityProvider, ProfileEventsEntityProvider, ProfileLinkEntityProvider, ProfileMessagingEntityProvider, ProfileStatusEntityProvider, PublishedAssessmentEntityProviderImpl, ReportDefEntityProvider, ShortenedUrlServiceEntityProviderImpl, SiteStatsMetricsEntityProvider, SynopticMsgcntrItemEntityProviderImpl, ValidationEntityProviderImpl

    public interface AutoRegister
    By implementing this interface you are telling the system to pick up all the objects which are implementing this interface and put them in a bucket so they will be loaded into any bean which implements BeanCollector and asks for them
    Author:
    Aaron Zeckoski (aaronz@vt.edu), Antranig Basman (antranig@caret.cam.ac.uk)
